Download Docker Toolbox
https://docs.docker.com/toolbox/toolbox_install_windows/

Set up Path for docker-machine.exe
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/39373217/docker-looks-something-went-wrong-in-step-looking-for-vboxmanage-exe

docker-machine create --driver azure --azure-subscription-id cc786216-c843-4350-ab79-a01e805af94c azure01

for userdefined paramenters 
https://docs.docker.com/machine/drivers/azure/#options

To setup the env for created docker-machine
docker-machine env azure01

To connect to the docker machine 
eval $(docker-machine env azure01)

Docker default port 2376 to change default port
--azure-open-port
